26#pragma once
27
28#include <VideoToolbox/VideoToolbox.h>
29#include "CMBaseObjectSPI.h"
30
31#if defined __has_include && __has_include(<CoreFoundation/CFPriv.h>)
32#include <VideoToolbox/VTVideoDecoder.h>
33#include <VideoToolbox/VTVideoDecoderRegistration.h>
34#else
35
36#ifdef __cplusplus
37extern "C" {
38#endif
39
40#pragma pack(push, 4)
41
42typedef FourCharCode FigVideoCodecType;
43typedef struct OpaqueVTVideoDecoder* VTVideoDecoderRef;
44typedef struct OpaqueVTVideoDecoderSession* VTVideoDecoderSession;
45typedef struct OpaqueVTVideoDecoderFrame* VTVideoDecoderFrame;
46
47typedef OSStatus (*VTVideoDecoderFunction_CreateInstance)(FourCharCode codecType, CFAllocatorRef allocator, VTVideoDecoderRef *instanceOut);
48typedef OSStatus (*VTVideoDecoderFunction_StartSession)(VTVideoDecoderRef, VTVideoDecoderSession, CMVideoFormatDescriptionRef);
49typedef OSStatus (*VTVideoDecoderFunction_DecodeFrame)(VTVideoDecoderRef, VTVideoDecoderFrame, CMSampleBufferRef, VTDecodeFrameFlags, VTDecodeInfoFlags*);
50typedef OSStatus (*VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD)();
51
52enum {
53 kVTVideoDecoder_ClassVersion_1 = 1,
54 kVTVideoDecoder_ClassVersion_2 = 2,
55 kVTVideoDecoder_ClassVersion_3 = 3,
56};
57
58typedef struct {
59 CMBaseClassVersion version;
60
61 VTVideoDecoderFunction_StartSession startSession;
62 VTVideoDecoderFunction_DecodeFrame decodeFrame;
63
64 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD copySupportedPropertyDictionary;
65 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD setProperties;
66
67 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD copySerializableProperties;
68 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD canAcceptFormatDescription;
69 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD finishDelayedFrames;
70 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD reserved7;
71 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD reserved8;
72 VTVideoDecoderFunction_TBD reserved9;
73} VTVideoDecoderClass;
74
75typedef struct {
76 CMBaseVTable base;
77 const VTVideoDecoderClass *videoDecoderClass;
78} VTVideoDecoderVTable;
79
80VT_EXPORT CMBaseClassID VTVideoDecoderGetClassID(void);
81VT_EXPORT CVPixelBufferPoolRef VTDecoderSessionGetPixelBufferPool(VTVideoDecoderSession session );
82VT_EXPORT OSStatus VTDecoderSessionSetPixelBufferAttributes(VTVideoDecoderSession session, CFDictionaryRef decompressorPixelBufferAttributes);
83VT_EXPORT OSStatus VTDecoderSessionEmitDecodedFrame(VTVideoDecoderSession session, VTVideoDecoderFrame frame, OSStatus status, VTDecodeInfoFlags infoFlags, CVImageBufferRef imageBuffer);
84VT_EXPORT OSStatus VTRegisterVideoDecoder(FigVideoCodecType, VTVideoDecoderFunction_CreateInstance);
85
86#pragma pack(pop)
